Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.92,0:00:14.97,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\blur1\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.15,0:00:15.74,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:19.27,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.27,0:00:22.96,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.96,0:00:26.58,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.58,0:00:30.34,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.34,0:00:33.51,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.88,0:00:36.64,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.64,0:00:40.10,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:44.90,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.90,0:00:48.27,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.27,0:00:50.90,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:54.49,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:00:59.28,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.28,0:01:02.62,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.24,0:01:11.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.88,0:01:14.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:16.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.01,0:01:19.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.85,0:01:24.86,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HFCFFFE&\b1\pos(472.971,156.105)}The Shinigami Chameleon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.85,0:01:24.86,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fscx100\fs110\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HFCFFFE&\b1\pos(480,675)}Showdown at the Old World's Fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.35,0:01:32.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Takeshi infiltrated Shocker's secret\Nbase in search of a mysterious steel box,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.48,0:01:35.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,but he was quickly exposed\Nand thrown into a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.18,0:01:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.54,0:01:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Rider-killer\Ntrap I arranged just for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.40,0:01:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.70,0:01:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A Rider-killer trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.69,0:01:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.51,0:01:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.61,0:02:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The walls are all\None meter thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.61,0:02:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider... I arranged them to be\Ntoo thick for you to break through
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.37,0:02:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,based on an analysis\Nof your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.46,0:02:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll run out of\Npower soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.21,0:02:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How long can I hold out?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.25,0:02:26.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider's superpowers\Ncannot last forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.28,0:02:30.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There are limits to the turbine-generated\Npower that he can store at one time,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.18,0:02:34.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and he needs to get his turbine to\Nspin again in order to generate more.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:39.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But in this tiny locked room\Nwith no wind and no way to drive,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.52,0:02:41.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,he can't get the\Nturbine to spin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.75,0:02:47.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We can see Rider's energy\Nfading before our very eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.79,0:02:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch the death of a\Nfool who opposed Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me, Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.12,0:03:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If you kill me now,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.22,0:03:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll never find the Nazi\Nbox you've been searching for!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.59,0:03:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Your desperation is pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.98,0:03:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you can\Nfool me that easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think it's a lie, check the\Nbox in Doctor Heinrich's possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.22,0:03:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.38,0:03:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't put it past\Nhim, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.26,0:03:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.81,0:03:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This box is a fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:03:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! The gun shot through it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.52,0:04:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The Nazi box was designed to\Nsurvive even a nuclear blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And the wavelength\Nmeter isn't responding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.75,0:04:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.02,0:04:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see I made my point.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo. Where's the real one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.77,0:04:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Release me, and I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Release him. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, speak.\NWhere is the Nazi box?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.67,0:04:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The real box...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.62,0:04:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Assistant Professor Abe Naoki of\NJonan University sent it to Doctor Oyama
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,in the engineering department\Nof Osaka Hanshin University.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.63,0:04:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The engineering department\Nof Osaka Hanshin University?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you escape\Nus, Hongo Takeshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.79,0:05:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.61,0:05:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, combatants of Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.78,0:05:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Use your talent and training\Nto kill Hongo Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.60,0:05:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Not good. I don't have\Nenough energy to fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone.\NHe can't have gotten far, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.11,0:05:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.67,0:05:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Yumi's\Nfather, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.06,0:06:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.16,0:06:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Search this room!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.21,0:06:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.18,0:06:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be a\Ndrainpipe up there...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.68,0:06:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our only chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.46,0:06:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there. You're safe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.20,0:06:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Am... Am I safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Yumi?\NWhere's my daughter, Yumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.78,0:06:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yumi is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.15,0:06:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.06,0:06:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.09,0:06:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And what happened\Nto the Nazi box?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.88,0:07:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Mr. Sunada.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.91,0:07:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the secret\Nof the Nazi box?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Just before the fall of Berlin,\Nthe dictator of Nazi Germany, Hitler,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.77,0:07:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,hid his treasure on\Nthe I-155 submarine
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.96,0:07:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and took it to their\Nally at the time, Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Only I, the submarine's\Ncaptain, knew about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.87,0:07:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitler's plan was\Nto escape to Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.33,0:07:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and use the trillions stored on\Nboard to rebuild the Third Reich.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.41,0:07:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But Hitler ended\Nup killing himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and the treasure has\Nremained in Japan, unused.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.36,0:07:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The location of the\Ntreasure is inside that box.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.49,0:07:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A treasure worth trillions...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker would surely want
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,to use it for evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.90,0:08:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi! You're all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.52,0:08:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing\Nhere in Lake Biwa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.36,0:08:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't just sit\Naround, doing nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.71,0:08:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So I followed you\Non a motorbike.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.14,0:08:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're absolutely incorrigible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.39,0:08:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.85,0:08:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.08,0:08:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that I could help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.76,0:08:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.07,0:08:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yumi's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.16,0:08:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The one you've\Nbeen worried about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.61,0:08:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunada, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.58,0:08:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad. I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.07,0:08:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.15,0:08:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from Yumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.44,0:09:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She asked me to give it\Nto you if I found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.32,0:09:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.85,0:09:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.22,0:09:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to take\NMr. Sunada somewhere safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.14,0:09:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Head to Osaka ahead of\Nme and meet with Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.37,0:09:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him what happened to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.63,0:09:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Sunada.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.90,0:09:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get you to Yumi's hospital\Nin Tokyo as soon as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.23,0:09:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and show her that\Nyou're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.72,0:09:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruriko! See you in Osaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:58.69,Sign,,0,0,0,,Hanshin Institute of Technology
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.42,0:10:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo was telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.71,0:10:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Oyama has the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I got dressed up as Doctor Oyama,\Nlike he asked...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.93,0:10:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,but Shocker still\Nhasn't shown themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.51,0:10:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No one saw that, did they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.56,0:10:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.71,0:10:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wonder what's\Ntaking Takeshi so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Takeshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Oyama here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.49,0:11:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Hongo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.97,0:11:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... nothing out\Nof the ordinary here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.23,0:11:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.47,0:11:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.20,0:11:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.95,0:11:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.67,0:11:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.92,0:12:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't act so surprised...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.80,0:12:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been waiting for\NShocker, and here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't waiting for Shocker...\NI was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.43,0:12:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Tachibana Tobei, Hongo Takeshi's\Nhelper and Shocker's hated enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.09,0:12:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And Midorikawa Ruriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.27,0:12:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So you knew it was me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That will speed things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to keep you\Nhere until Hongo arrives!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.70,0:12:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, show yourself!\NWhere did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.21,0:12:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:13:01.25,Bumper Episode 2-13,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\pos(355,520)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.15,0:13:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.56,0:13:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.33,0:13:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker took them both...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's open!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.23,0:13:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it open...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.91,0:13:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.47,0:13:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe there was a time when only Nazi\Nscience could make a box like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.31,0:13:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but that was 26 years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.09,0:13:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Science is advancing every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And Doctor Oyama is Hongo's mentor,\Nand a genius in electrophysics!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He opened that box ages ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.00,0:13:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.76,0:13:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say another word.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.54,0:13:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, hit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.57,0:14:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo already has the map\Nthat was inside that box.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.13,0:14:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Chameleon Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.74,0:14:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This foolish human will\Nmake a valuable hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You're going\Nto hold us hostage?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.42,0:14:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, hostages.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,To trade for Hongo's map.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.93,0:14:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather bite my tongue and die\Nthan go along with your schemes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.74,0:14:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Once they learn there's\Nnothing in that box,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.71,0:14:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker will make its next move.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.23,0:14:54.04,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Hongo, Tachibana Tobei and Midorikawa\NRuriko are in my possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.04,0:14:56.29,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,I'll trade them for the\Nmap in your possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:14:59.12,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,I'll be in Senri—Expoland,\Nthe old site of the world's fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.12,0:15:00.65,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Come at noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.10,0:15:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be there, Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A motorbike!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.24,0:15:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no one on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not here. Where's Hongo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.30,0:15:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.71,0:16:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You tricked me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the map\Nto the treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.93,0:16:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.12,0:16:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I will kill both of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.11,0:17:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This fight isn't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.50,0:17:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.37,0:17:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo, be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.32,0:17:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That monster can change\Ncolor, like a chameleon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.79,0:18:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not safe! Keep away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.11,0:18:10.61,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,I can't beat him unless I\Ntransform into Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.30,0:18:13.11,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,But if I transform now,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:14.73,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Ruriko will know everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:18.00,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,She'll know I'm a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.21,0:18:20.61,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,But I can't do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.08,0:18:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Hongo?\NFight me already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.44,0:18:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:42.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When wind spins the turbine in\Ncyborg Hongo Takeshi's belt,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.93,0:18:45.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,he transforms into\Nthe Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.12,0:18:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.92,0:18:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't possibly have\Nany more use for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.74,0:18:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.29,0:19:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider will\Nsurely show himself again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.01,0:19:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you to keep\Nhim from interfering.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.97,0:19:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the forest\Nshown in the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.01,0:19:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to see it... the treasure of\NHitler that's gone unused for 26 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.14,0:19:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here! Buried here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.75,0:19:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We've finally found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.41,0:19:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the trillions buried\Nhere will belong to Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.08,0:19:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker will become\Nstronger than ever before!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.82,0:20:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.78,0:20:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.55,0:20:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitler's treasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This has to be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.92,0:22:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me... was there really\Na Nazi treasure there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.92,0:22:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The treasure was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.11,0:22:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But I dug it up in advance\Nand threw it into the Pacific.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.85,0:22:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a tainted treasure,\Ngenerated by the evils of the human heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.91,0:22:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.31,0:22:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.28,0:22:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.96,0:22:46.75,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs76\bord4\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H2B3CA6&}Closed Today
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.20,0:22:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.31,0:22:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.89,0:22:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.75,0:23:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you glad to\Nhave your papa home?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.00,0:23:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hongo made this\Nhappen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.03,0:23:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.81,0:23:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.22,0:23:28.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi had foiled\NShocker's evil scheme.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.55,0:23:31.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,While enduring the pain\Nof his cyborg existence,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.48,0:23:35.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,he continues his\Nfight against evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.08,0:23:40.84,Cont,,550,0,150,,{\blur.8\fad(0,470)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.12,0:23:43.05,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(506.031,486.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.11,0:23:44.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.86,0:23:46.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is Bee Woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.19,0:23:50.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,People who buy glasses from a certain\Nstore are disappearing one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.57,0:23:52.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What is it about these glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.51,0:23:54.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What is Shocker\Nplotting this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.40,0:23:57.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week\Nfor more Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.27,0:24:00.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in "The Creepy Bee Woman!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.25,0:24:11.09,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.68,0:24:13.68,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.68,0:24:15.64,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.64,0:24:18.68,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.18,0:24:21.06,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.06,0:24:22.94,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.94,0:24:24.73,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.73,0:24:26.07,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.52,0:24:28.57,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.61,0:24:34.12,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.28,0:24:37.87,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.87,0:24:41.46,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.96,0:24:45.71,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!